        <p><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">日本札幌旅游攻略（交通篇）</span></strong></p>
<p><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">怎么去札幌？</span></strong></p>
<p><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">札幌市内交通？</span></strong></p>
<p><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">大鱼君为你一一解答。</span></strong></p>
<p><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-181-0.jpg" title="日本札幌旅游攻略（交通篇）_图片_0" alt="日本札幌旅游攻略（交通篇）_图片_0"></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.2000007629395px; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">飞机</span></strong><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">到札幌旅游十分方便。札幌有两个机场——新千岁机场和丘珠机场，分别有来自日本全国各地的班机，千岁机场更有班机来往于</span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">世界各大城市。直接乘机至新千岁机场，然后乘JR快车至札幌市。从东京成田机场、大阪、名古屋飞到札幌都只需要一个多小时，从福冈飞到札幌需要两个多小时。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">新千岁机场（New Chitose Airport）</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">位于日本北海道千岁市与苫小牧市交界，是札幌市的主机场，也是日本国内面积第一大的机场。目前，大中华地区飞往新千岁之航空业者有中国国际航空（北京）、中国东方航空（上海浦东）、中国南方航空（沈阳、大连、广州白云）、中华航空与长荣航空（台北桃园），以及国泰航空（香港）。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">机场交通<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（1）巴士：机场-札幌市内，每10-15分钟一班，时长80分钟，成人820日元，儿童410日元<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（2）JR日本铁路机场高速：机场-札幌站，每15分钟一班，时长36分钟，大人1040日元 儿童520日元<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（3）出租车：机场-札幌市内，时长60分钟，13000日元左右<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">机场有通往北海道各城市的公共汽车，包括支笏湖、洞爷湖、登别温泉和仁世户，十分便利<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">丘珠机场</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">丘珠机场位于北海道札幌市东区。根据日本空港整备法被分成地方管理机场，只是当地的一个较小的机场。</span></p>
<p><br style="word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">机场交通<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（1）大巴：机场-JR札幌站，时长25分钟，400日元<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">机场-地铁南北线麻生站，时长15分钟，200日元<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（2）出租车：机场-札幌站，时长25分钟，2500日元<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">机场-麻生站，时长15分钟，1500日元<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">机场-荣町站，时长3分钟，730日元<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.2000007629395px; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">轨道交通</span></strong><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">北海道所在的石狩平原铁路网密集，以札幌为中心，铁路通往四面八方。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">A、铁路（JR线）</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这是北海道内部交通的主要承担者，北海道内部各个城市之间都有JR线相连接，电车5-15分钟一班，十分迅捷。一条单行有轨电车线从大通出发，向西再向南走，绕行一圈回到薄野，单一票价为170日元。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">函馆本线：连接函馆、旭川、白石等地，同时也是北海道通往本州的主要干线<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">千岁线：连接札幌、桑园、白石、新千岁机场等地，是北海道内部的中心线路<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">札沼线（学园都市线）：路线与函馆本线并行<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">B、地铁</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">札幌地铁线路有三条，分别是南北线、东西线、东丰线，这些线路把札幌的政府区域、旅游景点、生活区域连接到一起。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">南北线：往返于麻生和真驹，共有16个站点（札幌，大通，中知岛等），颜色为绿色。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">东西线：往返于宫之泽和新札幌，共有19个站点（大通，东札幌，圆山公园等），颜色为橙色。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">东丰线：往返于荣町和福往，共有14个站点（月寒中央，大通，札幌等），颜色为蓝色。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">票价200日元起，一日通票800日元（周末则为每天500日元）。还有售价1000日元的一日通票，也可以乘坐有轨电车和公共汽车。还可以购买预先支付的“随你行”卡（With You Card，有各种面额），这种卡在地铁、公共汽车、有轨电车、じょうてつ及中央公共汽车上都能使用；与一日票不同，随你行卡不会在午夜作废。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">C、公交车</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">JR札幌站是当地公共汽车的主要终点站。札幌市市内的公交车线路跟地铁线几乎一样，方便了公交车和地铁之间的转乘。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">价格：起始200日元，按路程的长短收费<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">D、城市间高速巴士</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">城市间高速巴士是以札幌为中心，设有至函馆，旭川，知床等17条线路。除了拥有价格实惠的特点，还有深夜出发的班次可以满足您对于夜晚出行的意愿。使用车辆的坐席分为一排三座的可调式单人座位。深夜出发的班次还设有男女分区座位，即便是单身女性也可以放心使用。但由于线路有限，需要提前预约。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">E、观光车</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">共两条循环观光巴士线，「札幌散步巴士」及「Sapporo Walk」。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">札幌市内的散步巴士：途经北海道神宫、圆山动物园、大仓山滑雪跳高竞技场等札幌市中心及郊外值得一见的名胜风景，是环游札幌的最佳交通工具。但只在 4 月下旬至 10 月下旬运行。 <br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一天乘车证成人1000日元，小童500日元，一天内可无限次乘搭，运行时间由09:00- 17:40，每40分钟开出一班。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">另外，从札幌出发沿着小樽等地环游的路线中，还设有英语，汉语，汉语的导游服务，十分方便。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">官方网址：</span><a href="/fishtrip/japan/zhahuang/" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); text-decoration: underline; font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" target="_blank">http://www.tan90.cn/fishtrip/japan/zhahuang/</a><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">F、出租车</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">出租车起价为1.4公里520日元，里程费为每321米80日元，低速行驶时（时速低于10公里）每2分钟加收80日元，夜间行车（22：00至次日05：00）费用加收20％，冬季（12月10日至第二年的3月26日）出租车费用也加收20％。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;">G、租车/包车</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">经济条件允许，在国外自驾游也是相当不错的选择。办理租车业务的窗口在机场和车站。从大型车到小型车，种类丰富，而且还有最近备受关注的环保车。基本上都配备了导航系统。租借车辆需要有国际驾照等证明，请在出发之前确认。</span></p>
